# Copy to .env at your palace root (<palace_path>/.env) and fill in.
#
# Create a dedicated mempalace key (NOT reused from other projects — this
# gives you separate billing attribution and rotation) at:
#   https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
#
# Used by: mempalace link-author process (background edge authoring via
# an Opus-designed / Haiku-run jury — see docs/link_author_plan.md §2.8
# + docs/link_author_scheduling.md for the full setup).
#
# Rotation: revoke the key at console.anthropic.com, regenerate, and
# update this value. The next `mempalace link-author process` run picks
# up the new key without restarting the MCP server (the CLI reads .env
# on every invocation).
#
# Never commit this file with a real key. .env is in .gitignore.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
